---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Máquina de Produção — Vídeos Profissionais com IA" description="Pipeline completo de produção de vídeo com IA. Do roteiro à edição final.">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[80vh] flex items-center pt-20 pb-20 px-6 border-b border-gray-800 bg-grid-pattern overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#0a0a0a]/50 via-transparent to-[#0a0a0a]"></div>
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto w-full relative z-10 text-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border border-yellow-500/30 bg-yellow-500/10 text-yellow-500 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest px-4 py-1.5 mb-8 animate-fade-in-up">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.375 19.5h17.25m-17.25 0a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125M3.375 19.5h1.5C5.496 19.5 6 18.996 6 18.375m-2.625 0V5.625m0 12.75v-1.5c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125m18.375 2.625V5.625m0 12.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125m1.125-1.125v-1.5c0-.621-.504-1.125-1.125-1.125m0 3.75h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0118 18.375M20.625 4.5H3.375m17.25 0c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125M20.625 4.5h-1.5C18.504 4.5 18 5.004 18 5.625m3.75 0v1.5c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125M3.375 4.5c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125M3.375 4.5h1.5C5.496 4.5 6 5.004 6 5.625m-3.75 0v1.5c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125" /></svg>
        Máquina de Produção
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold font-industrial text-white uppercase tracking-tight leading-[1.1] mb-8 animate-fade-in-up">
        Vídeos profissionais com IA.<br>
        <span class="text-yellow-500">Do roteiro à edição final.</span>
      </h1>

      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 animate-fade-in-up">
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed">
          Um pipeline completo que transforma uma ideia em vídeo finalizado — narração, storyboard, imagens, clips, efeitos sonoros e timeline montada. Tudo orquestrado por IA dentro do Claude.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Pipeline visual minimalista -->
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 md:gap-4 flex-wrap mb-12 animate-fade-in-up">
        <span class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 border border-gray-700 px-3 py-1.5">Roteiro</span>
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" /></svg>
        <span class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 border border-gray-700 px-3 py-1.5">Storyboard</span>
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" /></svg>
        <span class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 border border-gray-700 px-3 py-1.5">Clips</span>
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" /></svg>
        <span class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 border border-gray-700 px-3 py-1.5">SFX</span>
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-500 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" /></svg>
        <span class="text-xs font-mono text-yellow-500 border border-yellow-500 px-3 py-1.5">DaVinci</span>
      </div>

      <a href="https://pay.hotmart.com/D105096667L" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group relative inline-block bg-yellow-500 hover:bg-yellow-400 text-black font-bold uppercase tracking-widest px-8 py-4 text-sm md:text-base transition-all animate-fade-in-up" style="clip-path: polygon(10px 0, 100% 0, 100% calc(100% - 10px), calc(100% - 10px) 100%, 0 100%, 0 10px);">
        Quero Começar
        <svg class="inline-block w-4 h-4 ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" /></svg>
      </a>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs mt-4 uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">
        12x de R$ 92,98 · Acesso imediato
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROVA: VÍDEO PRODUZIDO PELO PIPELINE -->
  <section class="py-24 px-6 border-b border-gray-800 bg-[#0a0a0a]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-yellow-500 font-mono text-sm mb-4">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5.25 5.653c0-.856.917-1.398 1.667-.986l11.54 6.348a1.125 1.125 0 010 1.971l-11.54 6.347a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.667-.985V5.653z" /></svg>
          Resultado Real
        </span>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold font-industrial text-white uppercase tracking-tight leading-none mb-4">
          1h45min da ideia à edição.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400">
          Este vídeo foi produzido inteiramente com o pipeline. Roteiro, imagens, clips, efeitos sonoros e timeline — tudo gerado por IA.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="relative aspect-video border border-gray-800 bg-[#111]">
        <iframe
          src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/JpTm3fFa4KQ"
          title="Vídeo produzido pela Máquina de Produção"
          allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
          allowfullscreen
          loading="lazy"
          class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full"
        ></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- O PROBLEMA -->
  <section class="py-24 px-6 border-b border-gray-800 bg-[#0f0f0f]">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="mb-16">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-yellow-500 font-mono text-sm mb-4">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
          O Problema
        </span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold font-industrial text-white uppercase tracking-tight max-w-3xl leading-none">
          Por que você ainda não produz vídeo.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 relative">
        <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-12 left-[16%] right-[16%] h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-900 via-yellow-900 to-red-900"></div>

        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <div class="relative z-10 bg-[#0a0a0a] p-8 border border-gray-800 hover:border-gray-600 transition-colors group">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-900/20 border border-green-700/50 mb-6 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-green-900/30 transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-green-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M18.364 18.364A9 9 0 005.636 5.636m12.728 12.728A9 9 0 015.636 5.636m12.728 12.728L5.636 5.636" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest font-industrial border-b border-gray-800 pb-4">01. O beco sem saída</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Você precisa de vídeo pra crescer. Mas produzir exige roteirista, designer, editor, motion designer — ou você fazendo tudo. Contratar é caro. Fazer sozinho consome o tempo que você não tem.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div class="relative z-10 bg-[#0a0a0a] p-8 border border-gray-800 hover:border-gray-600 transition-colors group">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-yellow-900/20 border border-yellow-700/50 mb-6 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-yellow-900/30 transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-yellow-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.813 15.904L9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 003.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 003.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09 3.09z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest font-industrial border-b border-gray-800 pb-4">02. A IA que só escreve</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            A maioria usa IA como um Google turbinado. Pede um texto, recebe um texto. Não sabe que a IA hoje gera imagens, cria clips de vídeo, transcreve áudio, monta timelines. O potencial existe — a ferramenta certa faltava.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <div class="relative z-10 bg-[#0a0a0a] p-8 border border-gray-800 hover:border-gray-600 transition-colors group">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-900/20 border border-red-700/50 mb-6 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-red-900/30 transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-red-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v3.75m-9.303 3.376c-.866 1.5.217 3.374 1.948 3.374h14.71c1.73 0 2.813-1.874 1.948-3.374L13.949 3.378c-.866-1.5-3.032-1.5-3.898 0L2.697 16.126zM12 15.75h.007v.008H12v-.008z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest font-industrial border-b border-gray-800 pb-4">03. O gap da execução</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Ter uma boa ideia de vídeo não é o problema. O problema é o caminho entre a ideia e o arquivo final no editor. Dezenas de passos, ferramentas diferentes, formatos, exportações. A maioria desiste no meio.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- O PIPELINE (SOLUÇÃO) -->
  <section class="py-24 px-6 border-b border-gray-800 bg-[#0a0a0a] relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/3 h-full bg-yellow-500/5 -skew-x-12 transform origin-top-right"></div>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative z-10">
      <div class="mb-16">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-yellow-500 font-mono text-sm mb-4">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11.42 15.17l-5.384 3.18A1 1 0 015 17.482V6.518a1 1 0 011.036-.868l5.384 3.18m0 0l5.384-3.18A1 1 0 0118 6.518v10.964a1 1 0 01-1.036.868l-5.384-3.18z" /></svg>
          O Pipeline
        </span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold font-industrial text-white uppercase tracking-tight max-w-4xl leading-none">
          Você conversa com a IA. Ela executa.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mt-6 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
          A Máquina de Produção roda dentro do Claude. Você conversa com a IA e ela executa cada fase da produção — não sugere, executa. Gera imagens, cria clips de vídeo, transcreve áudio, monta storyboards, exporta timelines. Tudo no seu computador.
        </p>
        <div class="h-1 w-24 bg-yellow-500 mt-6"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <!-- Bloco 1 -->
        <div class="bg-[#111] p-8 border border-gray-800 hover:border-yellow-500/50 transition-all">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="shrink-0 p-2 bg-black border border-gray-700">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0113.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375H8.25m0 12.75h7.5m-7.5 3H12M10.5 2.25H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v17.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 00-9-9z" /></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-white font-bold font-industrial uppercase tracking-tight">Roteiro com método</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            O sistema usa o método das 5 linhas — cinco frases que contam a história inteira antes de expandir pro roteiro completo. Narrativa com estrutura, não texto genérico.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Bloco 2 -->
        <div class="bg-[#111] p-8 border border-gray-800 hover:border-yellow-500/50 transition-all">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="shrink-0 p-2 bg-black border border-gray-700">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 15.75l5.159-5.159a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l5.159 5.159m-1.5-1.5l1.409-1.409a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l2.909 2.909M3.75 21h16.5a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25V5.25a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25H3.75A2.25 2.25 0 001.5 5.25v13.5A2.25 2.25 0 003.75 21z" /></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-white font-bold font-industrial uppercase tracking-tight">Storyboard visual</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Cada frase do roteiro vira uma cena com enquadramento, iluminação e atmosfera. Preview HTML antes de gastar um centavo em geração.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Bloco 3 -->
        <div class="bg-[#111] p-8 border border-gray-800 hover:border-yellow-500/50 transition-all">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="shrink-0 p-2 bg-black border border-gray-700">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.375 19.5h17.25m-17.25 0a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125M3.375 19.5h1.5C5.496 19.5 6 18.996 6 18.375m-2.625 0V5.625m0 12.75v-1.5c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125m18.375 2.625V5.625m0 12.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125m1.125-1.125v-1.5c0-.621-.504-1.125-1.125-1.125" /></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-white font-bold font-industrial uppercase tracking-tight">Imagens e clips por IA</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Keyframes gerados pelo Gemini com reference chaining — cada imagem usa a anterior como referência pra manter consistência. Depois, cada keyframe vira um clip de 5 segundos via fal.ai.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Bloco 4 -->
        <div class="bg-[#111] p-8 border border-gray-800 hover:border-yellow-500/50 transition-all">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="shrink-0 p-2 bg-black border border-gray-700">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.114 5.636a9 9 0 010 12.728M16.463 8.288a5.25 5.25 0 010 7.424M6.75 8.25l4.72-4.72a.75.75 0 011.28.53v15.88a.75.75 0 01-1.28.53l-4.72-4.72H4.51c-.88 0-1.704-.507-1.938-1.354A9.01 9.01 0 012.25 12c0-.83.112-1.633.322-2.396C2.806 8.756 3.63 8.25 4.51 8.25H6.75z" /></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-white font-bold font-industrial uppercase tracking-tight">Efeitos sonoros automáticos</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Camada de SFX alinhada com cada cena — passos, ambiente, máquinas, atmosfera. Gerados via ElevenLabs com timing sincronizado ao voice-over.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Bloco 5 (full width) -->
        <div class="bg-[#111] p-8 border border-gray-800 hover:border-yellow-500/50 transition-all md:col-span-2">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="shrink-0 p-2 bg-black border border-gray-700">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 17.25v1.007a3 3 0 01-.879 2.122L7.5 21h9l-.621-.621A3 3 0 0115 18.257V17.25m6-12V15a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 013 15V5.25m18 0A2.25 2.25 0 0018.75 3H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 003 5.25m18 0V12a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 013 12V5.25" /></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-white font-bold font-industrial uppercase tracking-tight">Timeline pronta pro editor</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Tudo vira um FCPXML: clips, voice-over e efeitos sonoros posicionados na timeline. Importa no DaVinci Resolve, Premiere Pro ou Final Cut. Ajusta transições, cor e música. Exporta.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- COMO FUNCIONA (8 PASSOS) -->
  <section class="py-24 px-6 border-b border-gray-800 bg-[#0f0f0f]">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="mb-16 text-center">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-yellow-500 font-mono text-sm mb-4">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 12h16.5m-16.5 3.75h16.5M3.75 19.5h16.5M5.625 4.5h12.75a1.875 1.875 0 010 3.75H5.625a1.875 1.875 0 010-3.75z" /></svg>
          Passo a Passo
        </span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold font-industrial text-white uppercase tracking-tight leading-none">
          Do zero ao vídeo em 8 passos.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="relative">
        <!-- Linha vertical conectora -->
        <div class="absolute left-6 md:left-8 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-gray-800"></div>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6 relative">
            <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-[#0a0a0a] border border-gray-700 flex items-center justify-center z-10">
              <span class="text-yellow-500 font-bold font-industrial text-lg">01</span>
            </div>
            <div class="pt-2 md:pt-4">
              <p class="text-white font-bold">Configura o branding da marca</p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Cores, estilo visual, tom de voz</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-6 relative">
            <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-[#0a0a0a] border border-gray-700 flex items-center justify-center z-10">
              <span class="text-yellow-500 font-bold font-industrial text-lg">02</span>
            </div>
            <div class="pt-2 md:pt-4">
              <p class="text-white font-bold">Cria o projeto e escreve o brief</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-6 relative">
            <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-[#0a0a0a] border border-gray-700 flex items-center justify-center z-10">
              <span class="text-yellow-500 font-bold font-industrial text-lg">03</span>
            </div>
            <div class="pt-2 md:pt-4">
              <p class="text-white font-bold">Desenvolve o roteiro com o método das 5 linhas</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-6 relative">
            <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-[#0a0a0a] border border-gray-700 flex items-center justify-center z-10">
              <span class="text-yellow-500 font-bold font-industrial text-lg">04</span>
            </div>
            <div class="pt-2 md:pt-4">
              <p class="text-white font-bold">Grava o voice-over</p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Ou gera com IA</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-6 relative">
            <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-[#0a0a0a] border border-gray-700 flex items-center justify-center z-10">
              <span class="text-yellow-500 font-bold font-industrial text-lg">05</span>
            </div>
            <div class="pt-2 md:pt-4">
              <p class="text-white font-bold">O sistema transcreve e monta o storyboard automaticamente</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-6 relative">
            <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-[#0a0a0a] border border-gray-700 flex items-center justify-center z-10">
              <span class="text-yellow-500 font-bold font-industrial text-lg">06</span>
            </div>
            <div class="pt-2 md:pt-4">
